parameters: It seems there are no traps in this area.
Heh heh heh, quite the collection, don't you think?
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[11]Why would you do such a thing...

To efficiently absorb spiritual power, it's necessary to
remove the barriers of the heart, this is an experiment for
that...

Of course, a bit of my personal taste is involved as well,
heh heh heh.

That's right, since you're here, why don't you cooperate as
well? Opportunities to study the spiritual power of a
Guardians' magical girl are quite rare, after all.

Just so happens there's one cross left over, I'll add you to
my collection as well.
Oh, are you going to help with the experiment again?
Would you like to view the defeat scene again?
Hmm... I didn't expect you to be this powerful...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[10]But, I can't possibly take so many kids with me at once...

I'll take those kids to the underground facility. I have
control over the security system there, so they'll be safer
inside the cells.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[10]That's kind of you, but... could it be that...

Of course, I will be expecting compensation for my
cooperation later on.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Oh, then please take this child with you as well...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Alright... I promise to protect you no matter what.

events.name: マッドサイエンティスト

parameters: Oh, have you decided to cooperate with my experiment?

Ah, it's the fruit of my research... I've successfully
developed something that can explosively increase spiritual
power.

It requires a bit of a procedure... How about it, will you
give it a try?
Heh heh heh, that's very honest of you.

Hmm, that's too bad... If you change your mind, feel free to
come by anytime.

If you ever feel like helping out with the experiment, come
by anytime.

"How is the condition of the engraved pattern? Please come
to report the results at any time."
Right, I have a nice gift for you.

However, you'll have to participate in a little experiment
for me... okay?

If you feel up to it, come here. I'll be waiting, heh heh
heh.
